name: Kydunk Cyberpunk City 2020
description: Kydunk Cyberpunk is an absorption of Javanese ritual behavior carried out in an effort to release all fear and panic and reaffirm the transcendental grip of Javanese people in this century. Kydunk Cyberpunk is the development of the song "Rumekso Ing Wengi" created by Sunan Kalijaga. Kidung is an old form of poetry, especially developed in the Javanese literary era of the Middle period, namely during the late Majapahit period. The song is usually sung at night, or after the evening prayer.
